OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1776777070
OL,3,CConstruction worker, 17, dies after
OL,4,Cbeing hit by concrete pipe
OL,6,FThe parents of teenager who died while
OL,7,Fworking on a new housing estate have
OL,8,Fcalled him "the most genuine, loving,
OL,9,Ffunny, caring lad you could ever wish
OL,10,Fto meet".
OL,12,FConstruction worker Shay Bladen was
OL,13,Fseverely injured when he was struck by
OL,14,Fa concrete pipe while working on a
OL,15,Fhousing development at Sniperley, near
OL,16,FDurham, on Thursday (16 April).
OL,18,FThe 17-year-old, from Witton Gilbert,
OL,19,Fwas taken to Newcastle's Royal
OL,20,FVictoria Infirmary, but died there on
OL,21,FFriday night.
OL,26,@pD@LOUrD@HO]
