CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1776777070
OL,3,CConstruction worker, 17, dies after
OL,4,Cbeing hit by concrete pipe
OL,6,FIn a tribute to their son, Lee and
OL,7,FSamantha said: "Shay was the most
OL,8,Fgenuine, loving, funny, caring lad you
OL,9,Fcould ever wish to meet, he lit up
OL,10,Fevery room making everyone smile even
OL,11,Fon the worst days.
OL,13,F"He was a genuine friend to many and
OL,14,Fthe most amazing, caring, big brother
OL,15,Fto Ellis and Edie.
OL,17,F"Shay loved to go boxing and go to the
OL,18,Fgym, he loved work and his job and
OL,19,Fjust constantly being on the go.
OL,26,@oD@POUuD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,426,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1776777070
OL,3,CConstruction worker, 17, dies after
OL,4,Cbeing hit by concrete pipe
OL,6,F"Shay also loved spending time with
OL,7,Fhis long-term girlfriend Libby.
OL,9,F"As his parents, we couldn't be more
OL,10,Fproud of the hard working, determined
OL,11,Fyoung man Shay turned out to be.
OL,13,F"We love you and seeing how highly
OL,14,Feveryone speaks about you just shows
OL,15,Fthe type of person you were.
OL,17,F"Our handsome brown eyed boy ` Forever
OL,18,F17."
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@AOUuD@AOUyD@AOUzD@DO]
