CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1776777070
OL,3,CConstruction worker, 17, dies after
OL,4,Cbeing hit by concrete pipe
OL,6,FDurham Constabulary and the Health and
OL,7,FSafety Executive are jointly working
OL,8,Fon an investigation.
OL,10,FDetective Chief Inspector Andy Crowe,
OL,11,Fwho is leading the inquiry, said:
OL,12,F"This has been a truly tragic incident
OL,13,Fand I would like to offer Shay's
OL,14,Ffamily and friends the sincere
OL,15,Fcondolences of everyone at Durham
OL,16,FConstabulary.
OL,26,@tD@AOU
