PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1776777070
OL,3,CConstruction worker, 17, dies after
OL,4,Cbeing hit by concrete pipe
OL,6,F"We are carrying out a joint
OL,7,Finvestigation with our colleagues at
OL,8,Fthe Health and Safety Executive to
OL,9,Fdetermine the exact circumstances as
OL,10,Fto how this tragedy has unfolded."
OL,12,FHealth and Safety Executive officers
OL,13,Fattended the site on Thursday.
OL,15,FAn HSE spokesperson said: "We are
OL,16,Finvestigating this incident alongside
OL,17,Four colleagues at Durham Police."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@bO]wD@[OUyD@aO]
